-- # Class: ApplicationError Description: Application Error events describe issues with an applications. The errormessage should be put in the event's <code>message</code> attribute. The<code>metadata.product</code> attribute can be used to capture the originatingapplication information. The <code>host</code> profile can used to include thegenerating device information. This class is helpful for applications thatgenerate or handle OCSF events and can also be used for errors in upstreamproducts and services.
