--     * Slot: duration Description: The event duration or aggregate time, the amount of time the event covers from<code>start_time</code> to <code>end_time</code> in milliseconds.
--     * Slot: end_time Description: The end time of a time period, or the time of the most recent event included inthe aggregate event.
