-- # Class: IncidentFinding Description: An Incident Finding reports the creation, update, or closure of securityincidents as a result of detections and/or analytics. <br><strong>Note:</strong><code>Incident Finding</code> implicitly includes the<code>incident</code> profile and it should be added to the<code>metadata.profiles[]</code> array.
