-- # Class: FileActivity Description: File System Activity events report when a process performs an action on a fileor folder.
--     * Slot: id
--     * Slot: access_mask Description: The access mask in a platform-native format.
--     * Slot: activity_id Description: The normalized identifier of the activity that triggered the event.
--     * Slot: component Description: <p>The name or relative pathname of a sub-component of the data object, ifapplicable. </p>For example: <code>attachment.doc</code>,<code>attachment.zip/bad.doc</code>, or<code>part.mime/part.cab/part.uue/part.doc</code>.
